featured_reviews.review_id: Very beautiful mosque of the locality and huge crowd is there specially on friday prayers.  Very good people as they have always helped me in keeping my helmets bags safely and take care of my belongings.  Reach before hand for Friday prayers as khutba starts @1:00 PM and namaz starts @ 1: 10 -1: 15 PM.  Spacious mosque with 2 floors.  But the road is very busy and mostly crowed before and after namaz so keep your vehicles at accessible places to get going after the prayer. Donate here as it will be beneficial as continous work and renovation are there and is done by donations by people.  Peaceful pace
